name: EoD CMs Full Clear
description:
Get yourself a spot for your weekly <:endofdragons:1181643239418237069> **End of Dragons** (Strike CMs) clear. We will be doing the following encounters:
<:maitrin:954126378511527986> **Aetherblade Hideout CM**
<:ankka:954126378473762866> **Xunlai Jade Junkyard CM**
<:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM**
<:oldlionscourt:1084190718022660188> **Old Lion's Court CM**
<:dragonvoid:954126378473767032> **Harvest Temple NM** (if time/mood permits).

<:quick_healer:1176639812900495400> <:alac_healer:1176639815282856017> **Healer Roles:**
- **Kiter**
  - Kite on <:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM** (high toughness is recommended).
- **Enforcer**
  - Tank Enforcer on <:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM** in the middle (while giving boons to the group).
- **Mindblade**
  - Tank Mindblade on <:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM** to the group.
- **Tank @ OLC**
  - Tank the watchknight on the stack at <:oldlionscourt:1084190718022660188> **Old Lion's Court CM**.
- **Off-Tank @ OLC**
  - Tank the watchknight off the stack at <:oldlionscourt:1084190718022660188> **Old Lion's Court CM**.

<:quick_healer:1176639812900495400> <:quick_dps:1176639849156051014> **Quickness Roles:**
- **Stability**
  - Give <:stability:844163847161774121> **Stability** to your subgroup on <:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM**.

<:dps:1176639819191951390> **DPS Roles:**
- **MechTank**
  - Tank (reliably!) the Mech Rider on <:ministerli:954126378364715059> **Kaineng Overlook CM**.

Let me know if you have any questions!
templateOverview: A template for an <:endofdragons:1181643239418237069> **EoD Strikes** full clear (with <:dragonvoid:954126378473767032> **Harvest Temple** on normal mode).
